nodes.text: The Muunilinst Podrace was a podrace event held in 0 ABY at the planet Muunilinst, at the outskirts of its capital Pilaan. It had six participants all funded by Muun gamblers who made bets on the race's outcome. The podrace was won by the Rebel Luke Skywalker, who's Podracer was provided by the gambler Nal Kenuun.
